Comment: 0,0:00:22.50,0:00:25.13,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Information, spreads in\Na matter of seconds.
Comment: 0,0:00:25.13,0:00:27.43,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,...but we don't know how to choose it.
Comment: 0,0:00:27.43,0:00:28.86,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who say, "Money\Ncan't buy my love..."
Comment: 0,0:00:28.86,0:00:31.32,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,...deserves a lariat three times.
Comment: 0,0:00:31.32,0:00:33.25,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,We make love according to the manuals.
Comment: 0,0:00:33.25,0:00:35.22,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't notice the lack of love.
Comment: 0,0:00:35.22,0:00:37.84,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Before we suffocate, let's yell. Ho!!!
Comment: 0,0:00:37.84,0:00:38.98,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,In the midnight dream.
Comment: 0,0:00:38.98,0:00:42.95,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,No place to relax in the sleepless city.
Comment: 0,0:00:42.95,0:00:46.89,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,We smile without dropping our guard.
Comment: 0,0:00:46.89,0:00:51.00,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,It's safe to lie and the truth is empty.
Comment: 0,0:00:51.00,0:00:55.05,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,I desperately wanna shut and break out.
Comment: 0,0:00:55.05,0:00:56.93,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, we gotta start.  Let's get moving.
Comment: 0,0:00:56.93,0:00:58.67,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's move into the brand new world.
Comment: 0,0:00:58.67,0:01:00.93,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's dive into the brand new trip.
Comment: 0,0:01:00.93,0:01:04.65,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,You're afraid of a big world.
Comment: 0,0:01:04.65,0:01:06.95,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just begun.
Comment: 0,0:01:06.95,0:01:08.92,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we go full speed and funky beat.
Comment: 0,0:01:08.92,0:01:10.65,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll surely shine.
Comment: 0,0:01:10.65,0:01:12.55,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Around the world.
Comment: 0,0:01:12.55,0:01:13.50,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Trip to the world.
Comment: 0,0:01:13.50,0:01:15.40,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo! Here we go to an unknown world.
Comment: 0,0:01:15.40,0:01:17.15,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a newborn traveler.
Comment: 0,0:01:17.15,0:01:19.20,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Unstable footsteps are fun to watch.
Comment: 0,0:01:19.20,0:01:21.30,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Get things done right, only when needed.
Comment: 0,0:01:21.30,0:01:22.82,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,So many people in this world...
Comment: 0,0:01:22.82,0:01:25.12,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,...sometimes, you'll receive slanders.
Comment: 0,0:01:25.12,0:01:27.16,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's warp uninteresting things...
Comment: 0,0:01:27.16,0:01:28.65,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,...and lead at least a rational life.
Comment: 0,0:01:28.65,0:01:30.43,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,That's our law.
