Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.95,0:03:20.74,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,1,300,000 yen ($13,000)\Nfor a 1991 model.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.74,0:03:23.85,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, the S13\Nis expensive.
Comment: 1,0:03:24.52,0:03:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\h
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.85,0:03:28.30,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Eight-Six after all.\NIt's more realistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.30,0:03:32.17,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The car has to be FR,\Nright, Takumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.17,0:03:33.01,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.94,0:03:36.10,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you listening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.10,0:03:38.05,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I am, Itsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.05,0:03:41.55,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,So, how much is\Nthat Eight-Six thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.55,0:03:43.90,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there's one\Nfor 300,000 ($3000).
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.90,0:03:45.20,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It needs the tag though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.20,0:03:47.25,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,And how much do you\Nhave saved so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.54,0:03:49.39,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,A little over 50,000 ($500).
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.39,0:03:51.66,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Long way to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.15,0:03:58.67,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Where can I find a good job\Nfor quick money?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.67,0:04:01.50,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I work full time this summer\Nat the station we're at...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.50,0:04:03.97,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...I can only earn 120,000 ($1200)\Nat most.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.97,0:04:06.68,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I can find\Na better paying job...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.08,0:04:09.67,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys have jobs?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.52,0:04:12.61,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Mogi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.65,0:04:20.93,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What, is it so surprising\Nfor me to talk to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.93,0:04:21.95,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.40,0:04:25.10,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,120,000 for full time\Nduring the summer?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.10,0:04:27.47,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,How long do you\Nwork a day?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.47,0:04:29.97,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,From the morning until the night!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.84,0:04:34.44,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You work that hard, and you\Nonly earn 120,000 a month?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.44,0:04:36.15,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a ballpark figure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.15,0:04:39.47,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Pay's really low for\Nhigh school students.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.40,0:04:44.97,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know.\NI've never had a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.01,0:04:50.90,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Work hard, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.90,0:04:53.56,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go out together when\Nfinals are over, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.31,0:04:55.35,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.81,0:04:59.50,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,She just said "go out together",\Ndidn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.50,0:05:00.28,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.28,0:05:01.82,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,With Mogi...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.15,0:05:04.92,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool, cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.92,0:05:07.69,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi, why didn't\Nyou tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.69,0:05:09.25,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You should've told me\Nthat you knew her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.25,0:05:13.35,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been almost a year since\NI last talked to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.35,0:05:15.95,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,We were in the same club...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.95,0:05:19.04,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...so we used to talk often,\Nuntil last summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.04,0:05:22.50,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talking about?\NIt doesn't matter anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.50,0:05:24.46,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Mogi Natsuki, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.46,0:05:26.47,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What a nice turn in the story!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.47,0:05:29.12,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,My eyes can't help following her.\NShe's so cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.10,0:05:36.94,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.94,0:05:38.15,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Takumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.15,0:05:39.30,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You look out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.30,0:05:42.79,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,We've gotta hurry!\NWe have a grammar test!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.79,0:05:43.86,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,H...hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.77,0:05:50.32,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, why don't we buy\Nan Eight-Six together?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.32,0:05:52.87,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If we combine our pay,\Nwe can pay the loan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.87,0:05:54.50,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.50,0:05:56.95,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you want a car so badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.95,0:05:59.65,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Your family has one, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.65,0:06:01.05,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.05,0:06:04.65,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad's car is automatic\Nand front wheel drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.65,0:06:07.45,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,And the engine is diesel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.45,0:06:10.64,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It sucks.\NIt's not even a car.{Hiro agrees.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.18,0:06:15.73,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If it runs on four tires, it's a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.73,0:06:17.69,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.69,0:06:21.59,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's not enjoyable on the mountain\Npasses, I don't call it a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.59,0:06:23.68,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you do on the\Nmountain passes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.96,0:06:25.66,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.66,0:06:27.66,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Tackle the corners!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.66,0:06:29.33,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The corners?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.33,0:06:31.75,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it fun doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.75,0:06:33.71,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.71,0:06:38.86,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a man, and you don't want to tackle\Nthe corners on the mountain passes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.86,0:06:42.26,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tired of that kind of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.26,0:06:44.35,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.35,0:06:47.43,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,We just got our licenses\Nlast month.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.60,0:07:05.82,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.82,0:07:08.82,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You look best in your uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.82,0:07:09.81,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.81,0:07:11.20,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.04,0:07:19.67,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa, my schoolmate has a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.67,0:07:27.82,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he works throughout the summer,\Nhe'll only earn 120,000 or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.82,0:07:30.50,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's about right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.50,0:07:34.82,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's hard to earn money.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.82,0:07:40.32,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I receive 300,000 ($3000) a month\Nby only seeing you three times.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.15,0:07:43.81,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it alright to get that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.81,0:07:47.75,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's alright, because you're worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.58,0:07:52.08,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it?  I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.96,0:07:56.50,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.50,0:07:58.42,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}Thank you very much.{\r}\NThank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.42,0:08:03.89,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Takumi, think about\Nthe Eight-Six, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.89,0:08:06.36,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about the Eight-Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.36,0:08:09.35,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys have good taste...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.35,0:08:11.47,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...looking at an Eight-Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.49,0:08:13.30,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, right, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.30,0:08:15.94,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so, too, Iketani?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.94,0:08:18.32,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, the Eight-Six is a good car.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.32,0:08:19.77,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,See?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.77,0:08:24.99,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, to tell the truth, I don't know\Nanything about the Eight-Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.99,0:08:27.20,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Who makes it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.20,0:08:31.19,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious, Takumi?\NWanna drink some high octane?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.19,0:08:35.61,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pitiful for someone working at a gas station\Nnot to know about the Eight-Six!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.61,0:08:38.28,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.28,0:08:43.05,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,When you guys were in 3rd or 4th grade,\Nthe 92 was already available.
Comment: 1,0:08:38.28,0:08:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0440,,\h
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.05,0:08:46.57,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,There's an old car we use\Nfor work, at my place...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.57,0:08:48.30,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't compare it with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.30,0:08:50.89,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's old, the Eight-Six is different!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.67,0:08:54.84,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If I bought an Eight-Six,\Ncould I join your team?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.84,0:08:58.37,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been dreaming of joining\Nthe Akina Speedstars!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.37,0:08:59.50,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.50,0:09:04.57,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, it's Saturday, so people\Nwill be gathering on Mt. Akina tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.57,0:09:05.86,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna come along?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.50,0:09:07.99,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.67,0:09:11.19,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,But... we don't have a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.19,0:09:12.78,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you a ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.52,0:09:19.04,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,In your S13?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.04,0:09:21.56,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I will, I will!\NI'll definitely go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.56,0:09:23.84,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going, right, Takumi?  We don't\Nget a chance like this very often!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.84,0:09:26.85,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}Yahoo, I'll join the Speedstars!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.41,0:09:27.80,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't say I was going.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.14,0:09:34.07,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,We're leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.07,0:09:37.41,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, and I'll pick you up\Nat the bus station at 8:00pm!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.41,0:09:38.10,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.87,0:09:42.86,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really into it.  Which mountain\Npass are you going to?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.86,0:09:47.16,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Manager, Mt. Akina is the only place\Nto drive around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.16,0:09:51.20,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Our team is proud of being\Nthe fastest on Mt. Akina.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.20,0:09:54.37,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,There are many guys who proclaim\Nthemselves the fastest on Mt. Akina.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.97,0:09:56.80,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was actively driving...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.80,0:10:00.38,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...there was a guy everyone knew\Nwas the fastest on Mt. Akina.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.38,0:10:04.38,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,And he's still driving on Mt. Akina.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.38,0:10:05.83,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.83,0:10:11.30,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I know most of the people driving on Mt. Akina,\Nbut I don't know anyone that old.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.30,0:10:15.16,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't drive at the\Nsame time you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.16,0:10:18.85,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He's an old guy, who\Nruns a tofu shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.69,0:10:25.24,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He delivers tofu to the hotel\Nby Akina Lake around 4:00am.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.24,0:10:29.22,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,His speed on the downhill\Nis well worth watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.22,0:10:32.99,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He has to drive in rain and snow,\Nbecause it's his job.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.99,0:10:37.85,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's Akina, he knows everything,\Neven the stains on the asphalt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.46,0:10:43.36,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet the fastest on Mt. Akina is\Nthe Eight-Six from a tofu shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.36,0:10:45.42,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The Eight-Six from\Na tofu shop?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.64,0:10:55.02,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going out, Takumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.02,0:10:57.78,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm supposed to\Nmeet with Itsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.78,0:10:59.50,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind you\Nstaying out late...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.50,0:11:01.58,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I'll beat you until you\Nwake up in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.58,0:11:04.02,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.  You don't have to tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.02,0:11:05.33,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.88,0:11:26.77,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, Takumi!\NYou'll disturb Iketani!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.77,0:11:30.40,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you say so,\Nwhat's scary is scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.40,0:11:31.85,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.85,0:11:34.60,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's scared when\Nriding with a Road Racer.{speedster, road racer, whatever appropriate.}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.60,0:11:37.08,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, it's a hairpin\Ncurve in 2nd gear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.06,0:11:46.07,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, Takumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.24,0:11:51.85,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, I'll push a\Nlittle harder tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.85,0:11:53.07,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's go full tilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.50,0:11:58.39,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright, Takumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.39,0:12:00.65,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect you\Nto be so scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.65,0:12:03.20,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...so I pushed hard without\Nworrying about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.30,0:12:07.83,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a wimp!\NYou're so uncool!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.83,0:12:11.50,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be one of those people\Nwho screams on a roller coaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.50,0:12:15.29,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never thought a\Nroller coaster was scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.29,0:12:17.60,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.60,0:12:22.02,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Itsuki, you wouldn't\Nunderstand this fear...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.02,0:12:24.02,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...even if I explained it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.43,0:12:40.50,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I've never seen them before...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.50,0:12:43.03,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Are they heading for\NMt. Akina at this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.50,0:12:47.45,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Something might be\Nhappening at the peak.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.81,0:13:00.72,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Never seen them before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.81,0:13:14.50,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Redsuns...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.50,0:13:17.41,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Are they the Redsuns,\Nthe fastest on Akagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.85,0:13:45.23,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the members of the\NAkagi Redsuns team.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.23,0:13:47.47,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate to ask this so\Nabruptly, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.47,0:13:52.90,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...if you know any team or driver who's\Nthe fastest on this mountain, let us know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.90,0:13:53.78,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.78,0:13:54.40,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It should be us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.77,0:13:58.90,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the Akina Speedstars team...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.90,0:14:00.91,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...and we consider ourselves the fastest here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.17,0:14:04.23,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That makes it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.23,0:14:09.13,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to hold a "gathering" with\Nthe Akagi Redsuns on this mountain?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.00,0:14:17.01,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it's gonna be a cool scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.70,0:14:19.35,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.35,0:14:22.97,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's boring, always driving\Nagainst people you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.97,0:14:26.69,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's exciting to drive\Nwith other teams.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.69,0:14:29.45,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You can make new friends,\Nand exchange information.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.45,0:14:31.68,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll help improve both\Nof our skill levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.68,0:14:33.45,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll drive along for a while,\Nthen pick one from each team...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.45,0:14:37.02,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...and race uphill and\Ndownhill at the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.02,0:14:42.14,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not concerned about winning or losing,\Njust friendship between teams.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.14,0:14:42.83,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,How does it sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.83,0:14:46.31,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's what it is, we don't have\Nany reason to decline.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.31,0:14:47.46,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.46,0:14:50.92,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,How does next Saturday\Nat 10:00pm sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.92,0:14:52.38,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.38,0:14:56.38,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll drive as much\Nas we can today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.38,0:14:58.84,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,This is awesome,\Nso awesome, Takumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.12,0:15:11.19,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have to hold back!\NLet's get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.19,0:15:11.86,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.64,0:15:24.96,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Iketani...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.69,0:15:30.46,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see how the Takahashi brothers,\Nthe fastest on Akagi, drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.66,0:15:32.17,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi brothers...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.17,0:15:34.35,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mean they're the super famous\NTakahashi brothers...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.35,0:15:35.80,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...the ones who were covered\Nin the magazine?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:35.80,0:15:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0440,,{\fs20\c&HA0A0A0&\1a&H50&}rotary:  reference to the Wankel engine used by Mazda
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.80,0:15:39.76,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, people call them the Takahashi\Nbrothers of the rotary engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.86,0:15:43.72,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Iketani, what about us?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.72,0:15:48.01,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I drive alone\Nwhen I drive seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.01,0:15:50.44,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait here,\NI'll pick you up later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.08,0:16:02.50,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel left out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.50,0:16:05.95,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are we the only ones\Nwho don't have a car?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.79,0:16:09.17,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Itsuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.17,0:16:12.33,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...is it so fun to be a Road Racer?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.33,0:16:17.98,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do they get so excited\Nabout such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.98,0:16:19.84,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who has to wonder!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.84,0:16:23.30,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hearing the sounds of cars\Nbeing pushed to the limit...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.30,0:16:26.68,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...don't you get excited, Takumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.48,0:16:29.65,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Excited...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.85,0:16:33.67,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Fujiwara Tofu Shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.11,0:16:37.44,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's you, Yuichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.44,0:16:39.66,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the call\Nin the middle of the night?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.66,0:16:40.95,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,"It's you" you said?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.95,0:16:43.62,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while, and you sound so cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.55,0:16:47.85,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I passed you coming back\Nfrom your delivery.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.35,0:16:50.54,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I flashed my lights,\Nbut you ignored me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.54,0:16:53.74,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that wasn't me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.74,0:16:56.47,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}It had to be, because the car was your Eight-Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.10,0:17:00.04,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.04,0:17:03.51,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It was probably my car,\Nbut I wasn't driving.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.94,0:17:07.08,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}My son, Takumi, is delivering\Ntofu to the hotel now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.35,0:17:10.81,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,S...say what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.81,0:17:12.79,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}S...since when?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.09,0:17:14.73,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Five years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.73,0:17:16.00,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,"Five years ago...?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.00,0:17:17.99,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,When he was only 7th grade?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.20,0:17:17.99,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,0)}{\a6\c&HA0A0A0&\fs20}(Note:  Japan's legal driving age is 18.)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.30,0:17:39.05,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, I can't keep up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.55,0:17:45.75,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}They're fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.75,0:17:49.67,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I'm pushing myself to the limit, and I can't\Ncatch any of the Redsuns.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.32,0:17:59.22,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.72,0:18:01.25,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,They're pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.25,0:18:04.01,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Even our second stringers\Ncould beat them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.01,0:18:06.55,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have to send\Nour best next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.55,0:18:07.70,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pass on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.97,0:18:10.60,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If you won't, then I'll pass, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.60,0:18:12.51,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you should drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.51,0:18:17.21,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave a course record that the\Nlocal guys can never beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.21,0:18:21.07,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, the name of the Akagi\NRedsuns won't become legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.35,0:18:26.75,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,For starters, we'll rewrite every\Ncourse record in this prefecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.75,0:18:31.08,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Soon, we'll do the same in Saitama,\NKanagawa, Tokyo, and Chiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.08,0:18:37.11,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be legendary Road Racers, leaving the fastest\Nrecords in the Kanto area, then retire.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.11,0:18:42.11,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the Akagi Redsuns'\N"Fastest in Kanto Project."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.78,0:19:00.42,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible.  They're\Nfundamentally different.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.42,0:19:05.38,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so shocking to be outrun\Nby outsiders on our home ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.68,0:19:09.06,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,They've spent a lot of money on their\Nsuspension, and they've got power, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.06,0:19:11.59,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible to compete\Nwith the Redsuns.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.59,0:19:14.58,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,But the local people can't run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.58,0:19:17.34,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.  Since we said\N"yes," we have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.34,0:19:20.18,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,But you can't beat them with just guts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.18,0:19:22.70,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's...  But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.68,0:19:28.12,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's getting late, so let's find a place\Nto talk about this tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.04,0:19:32.78,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Road Racers hate defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.78,0:19:36.66,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,So when it comes to racing,\Nwe tend to become overly stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.66,0:19:41.40,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing could be worse than being defeated\Nby outsiders on our home ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.17,0:19:45.83,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like the code of the Road Racer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.35,0:19:57.98,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where's Ryosuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.36,0:20:00.00,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He went home a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.00,0:20:02.18,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the only ones still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.48,0:20:04.32,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be dawn soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.64,0:20:07.20,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.39,0:20:22.10,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,They can't keep up with me\Nif I drive seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.10,0:20:23.92,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,They aren't so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.58,0:20:30.10,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,There's somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.76,0:20:38.99,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not from our team.\NIs it an MR2 or a 180?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.72,0:20:56.12,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.  You won't be in my mirror\Nafter two more corners!
