Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.70,0:21:40.57,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I having a bad dream or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.57,0:21:41.59,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
