Comment: 0,0:23:49.20,0:23:50.99,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Knock down in comma zero one second.
Comment: 0,0:23:50.99,0:23:53.24,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,You head for the next town, leaving trails.
Comment: 0,0:23:53.24,0:23:55.30,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Dust rises and the loser falls down to the ground.
Comment: 0,0:23:55.30,0:23:56.85,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,The puffery, full of logic...
Comment: 0,0:23:56.85,0:23:58.91,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,...is bothering, so let's ignore it.
Comment: 0,0:23:58.91,0:24:00.85,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,The streaker disappears into the street.
Comment: 0,0:24:00.85,0:24:02.25,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Something they would know.
Comment: 0,0:24:02.25,0:24:03.50,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Rage your dream.
Comment: 0,0:24:03.50,0:24:06.25,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,In the never-ending street...
Comment: 0,0:24:06.25,0:24:10.25,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,...without looking back at your love or your past...
Comment: 0,0:24:10.25,0:24:14.25,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,...you keep on going, so you shine.
Comment: 0,0:24:14.25,0:24:15.35,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Rage your dream.
Comment: 0,0:24:15.35,0:24:19.17,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,You live in the present.
